Hi,
	I've done some changes at LBL to the latest version of BIND:

	1) The resolver completes partial names entered by the users.
	   It allows a system and a user defined alias files.

	2) Gethostbyaddr is modified to send a request in the special
	   IN-ADDR.ARPA domain if the name server can't find the 
	   information in local cache.

	I hope you take a look at these features and welcome any comments.
	The changes can be ftp'ed from lbl-csam :
	 
	   user : ftp
	   password : immaterial
	   directory : pub/bind

	-- chinheng@lbl-csam

